This is to inform you that Independent Directors of the company at their Separate Meeting held today i.e. on Friday, 20th March, 2026 from 3:45 P.M. to 4:10 P.M. at the Registered Office of the Company, inter alia, has reviewed and considered:

1. The performance of Non-Independent Directors and the Board of Directors;

2. The performance of the Chairperson of the Company; 

3. Assessed the quality, quantity and timeliness of flow of information ....

